reviewText: This version is in Swedish and is not so labeled in the description.  It does not play in my DVD player.  The product is worthless, but Amazon stood behind it! I was given full credit and no fuss in a return.

Not sure what format this is, but it simply doesn't work. I tried exchanging it for another copy of the same DVD and had the same problem. I tried it on 2 different DVD players in my house and it still doesn't work. This is not your standard DVD format so be cautious when purchasing.
